  "texts": [
    "At each iteration, we select the top N images based on their Sscore(s) and add them to D L while removing them from D U.",
    "The Fig. 2 shows the algorithm.",
    "To enhance the selection of images for Active Learning, we propose using the Prediction Probabilities of images in image classification.",
    "Firstly, we train an Image Classification Model using labeled images.",
    "We then use this model to predict the labels of images in D U that are not labeled."
  ]
